    "bodyHtml": "<p><em>Modern Individualism<sup>[50]</sup> characteristic of today’s Bonsai Ego,<sup>[51]</sup> Individualism is idiotic.<sup>[52]</sup></em><em> </em><strong><em>Individual Integrity versus Individual Autonomy</em></strong></p><p><strong><em>Individualism verses Sound Metaphysical Hierarchy &amp; True Freedom</em></strong>                      </p>"
