    "index": 99,
    "title": "Assyrian Captivity (733 BCE -722 BCE)",
    "slug": "assyrian-captivity-733-bce-722-bce",
    "bodyHtml": "<p><strong><em>The earliest Israelite “Exile” was that of the Assyrian Captivity during the in the period between 733 BCE and 722 BCE, which was followed by the destruction of the First Temple and the “Exile” of the Judaeans in the Babylonian Captivity, which began in 597 BCE and again in 586 BCE.</em></strong></p><ul><li><strong><em>Empty Section in Volume 17 (no text; only section title) </em></strong></li><li><strong><em>Empty Section in Volume 15 (no text; only section title) </em></strong></li></ul>"
