    "slug": "deuteronomy-prophet-the-paraclete",
    "bodyHtml": "<p>This “true Prophet” of the Maccabees was <strong>the Deuteronomy Prophet</strong>,<sup>[103]</sup> about whom we will speak in Volumes Twelve and Sixteen. <strong>The Paraclete</strong><sup>[104]</sup></p>"
